<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.11">
<l>aṟivariya pirāṉai yāḻiyaṅkaiyaṉai yēyalaṟṟi</l>
<l>naṟiyanaṉ malarnāṭi naṉkurukūrccaṭakōpaṉ coṉṉa</l>
<l>kuṟikoḷā yirattuḷ ḷivaipattun tirukkuṟuṅ kuṭiyataṉmē</l>
<l>laṟiyak kaṟṟuvallār vaiṭṭaṇavarāḻkaṭal ñālattuḷḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who learn by heart  [and] master</l> 
<l>these ten on Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi among the meaningful thousand</l>
<l>composed by Caṭakōpaṉ from good Kurukūr, seeking fragrant good blossoms,</l>
<l>talking incessantly of him whose hand [holds] the discus, the lord difficult to understand,</l>
	<l>[are] Vaiṣṇavas in the world [surrounded] by the deep ocean.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
